OL,3,CTwo men charged in connection with
OL,4,Cfatal shooting in Clapham
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a murder investigation
OL,8,Fin Clapham.
OL,10,FOn the night of the 8th September
OL,11,F2025, the Metropolitan Police were
OL,12,Fcalled to reports of a shooting.
OL,14,FA 27 year old man, Kyrone Moodie was
OL,15,Ftreated at the scene, before being
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital where he died the
OL,17,Fnext day.
OL,19,FKyrone's family continue to be
OL,20,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
