OL,3,CTwo men charged in connection with
OL,4,Cfatal shooting in Clapham
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, 22 April, police
OL,7,Farrested a 20 year old man at an
OL,8,Faddress in Lambeth on suspicion of
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FA 31 year old man was detained
OL,12,Fyesterday, Thursday, 23 April, on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of perverting the course of
OL,14,Fjustice.
OL,16,FMoureik Ebanks has been charged with
OL,17,Fmurder, attempted murder and
OL,18,Fpossession of a firearm.
OL,20,FRushaune Davis has been charged with
OL,21,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
